data.description: Exceptionally Private Corner, 2-story townhome in gated Boca Pointe Country Club (no mandatory membership!) Split level entrance opens up to a bright living area w/ vaulted high ceiling, dining, family room and kitchen area, plus 1/2 bath & a fabulous private patio & IMPACT windows!  Upstairs features 2 private bedrooms w/ 2 full baths, and small loft for a desk. Primary Bath enjoys gorgeous marble finishes & jacuzzi tub. New wood flooring throughout. Washer and dryer are inside w/ ample storage!  1 assigned parking space & plenty of guest parking. RENTALS allowed 4 times per yr w/ no wait period! Boca Pointe enjoys Top Rated Schools (Verde Elementary, Boca Middle and Boca High) - a favorite among buyers looking for the area's top schools! Quick walk to Resort style community pool & hot tub Membership at The Club at Boca Pointe is an optional membership available to residents of the Boca Pointe community. The club offers the very best of the Boca Raton area and beyond. As a Member you'll enjoy access to the private 18 hole championship golf course, state of the art  fitness center, pickleball, tennis, and a host of dining venues and social events for every occasion.
